### 01. 댓글 생성 (최상위)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks/{{taskPublicId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "테스트 댓글입니다."
}

### 02. 대댓글 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks/{{taskPublicId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "테스트 대댓글입니다.",
  "parentCommentId": {{parentCommentId}}
}

### 03. 댓글 목록 조회 (계층형)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks/{{taskPublicId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 04. 댓글 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectPublicId}}/tasks/{{taskPublicId}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newContent": "수정된 댓글 내용입니다."
}